headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Predicting Freeport-McMoRan Stock Will Climb or Sink?
summary: Despite Freeport-McMoRan's strong performance relative to the broader market over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a cautiously optimistic outlook about the stock’s prospects.
